{
  "metadata": {
    "synopsis": "One of the memories available in the Colony \"Brain Reader\" depicts an example memory, of Balthazar experimenting on a thrall in order to try out the brain reading device. The memory belongs to an enthralled subject.",
    "how_to_trigger": "- Load up GustavDev/SCL_Main_A- Use ReCon command \"oe MemLib_AllJars\" to get all the brain jars and teleport to the Brain Reading Device.- In front of you will be a severed head and a receptacle to its left. Insert the appropriate brain jar into the receptacle by interacting with it - the jar is called \"Willing Mind\".- After inserting the jar, it will appear on top of the receptacle and you can talk to the severed head for the dialogue to start."
  },
